# **🧭 Choose Your Mode (Card Grid)**

LC — Foundations

For first‑time users. Filing hygiene, timelines, service, relief, evidence.

LCA — Advanced

Complex litigation. Lawfare resistance, TRO/PI, Younger, record‑first strategy.

FG — Field Guide

1‑page task cards (serve by mail, compute time, tailor relief, etc.).

FGA — Field Guide Advanced

Deep‑dive cards for edge cases and expert workflows.

JC — Judicial Calculus

Map system behavior; appeals posture; archive‑as‑remedy.

LCa — Lawyer Calculus

Clinics/pro bono workflows, QA checklists, review templates.

