**🔧 Nesting Guide (for existing homepage)**

1. Create a sub‑page under your current homepage → “LCES Home (New).”
2. Paste this entire template into that sub‑page.
3. Add a synced block with your top nav (Start Here + Choose Your Mode). Paste the synced block into related sub‑pages.
4. Add Linked databases: show a filtered view of Rule Specs, Service Ledger, Updates Log on the homepage.
5. Move the “What’s New” section above the fold; show recent 3.
6. Attach the Law as Computation PDF in the module section.
7. When stable, Replace your old homepage link with this page.

